               <p>Prisoner's defence. I bought these pigs; I gave fourteen pounds for them, and took a receipt from him. <rs id="t18020428-84-verdict444" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-84-verdict444" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 42.</p>
